name: AeroplaneSounds(withDing&FlapSounds)
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: aeroplane sounds
des:
If you love the ambient sounds you hear in a flight, like dings and wing flaps, then this is the perfect sound for you.

Simply say 'Alexa, open aeroplane sounds' to help you sleep as if you're in a flight!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
